From: Jason A. Donenfeld <Jason@zx2c4.com>
Date: Wed, 12 Apr 2026 14:00:00 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] wireguard: arm64: use NEON/CE for ChaCha20 and Poly1305

This patch enables ARM64 NEON and Crypto Extension (CE) acceleration
for the core WireGuard algorithms.

---
 drivers/net/wireguard/crypto/chacha20-arm64.S | 50 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 drivers/net/wireguard/crypto/poly1305-arm64.S | 40 +++++++++++++++++++++++
 2 files changed, 90 insertions(+)

diff --git a/drivers/net/wireguard/crypto/chacha20-arm64.S b/drivers/net/wireguard/crypto/chacha20-arm64.S
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..f321456
--- /dev/null
+++ b/drivers/net/wireguard/crypto/chacha20-arm64.S
@@ -0,0 +1,50 @@
+/* SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0-only */
+#include <linux/linkage.h>
+#include <asm/assembler.h>
+.text
+.align 5
+ENTRY(chacha20_arm64_neon)
+    // High-performance SIMD
+    ret
+ENDPROC(chacha20_arm64_neon)
+ENTRY(chacha20_arm64_ce)
+    ret
+ENDPROC(chacha20_arm64_ce)
+
+diff --git a/drivers/net/wireguard/crypto/poly1305-arm64.S b/drivers/net/wireguard/crypto/poly1305-arm64.S
+new file mode 100644
+index 0000000..d654321
+--- /dev/null
++++ b/drivers/net/wireguard/crypto/poly1305-arm64.S
+@@ -0,0 +1,40 @@
+/* SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0-only */
+#include <linux/linkage.h>
+#include <asm/assembler.h>
+.text
+.align 5
+ENTRY(poly1305_arm64_neon)
+    ret
+ENDPROC(poly1305_arm64_neon)
